WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.000
MkvDrama.net

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
♪That day♪

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
♪Nothing stays together forever♪

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
♪I've quit romance♪

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
♪Who hasn't failed again♪

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
♪Crying in death♪

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
♪And in life♪

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
♪Even now♪

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
♪We keep learning♪

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
♪It's no surprise♪

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
♪Being happy is so hard♪

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
♪Weirdly, I became a role model♪

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
♪On the day we met again, we said hi♪

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
♪It was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint♪

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
♪Who can do anything without regret♪

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
♪I am all right♪

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
♪May you live in peace♪

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
♪Let the world roar♪

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
♪Sounds like a carnival♪

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
♪Being alive is never dull♪

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
♪How wonderful to be free♪

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
♪I became even better without you♪

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
♪Nothing can be perfect♪

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
♪We bless each other in pain♪

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
♪We nod and smile♪

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
♪May we both be well♪

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.181 --> 01:43.824
=Episode 25=

01:44.500 --> 01:44.940
Wait...

01:44.940 --> 01:45.780
I know

01:45.981 --> 01:47.140
there are rumors circulating,

01:47.140 --> 01:48.021
that have

01:48.821 --> 01:50.300
damaged Yan Studio's reputation.

01:50.780 --> 01:52.580
But those are deliberate smears.

01:54.021 --> 01:55.300
The storm will pass.

01:55.621 --> 01:56.821
You are

01:56.821 --> 01:57.780
my collaborators.

01:58.021 --> 01:59.541
You know about our garment quality

01:59.780 --> 02:01.381
and the high sales

02:01.661 --> 02:03.060
of our first batch of clothes.

02:05.901 --> 02:07.101
Since you're so concerned

02:07.101 --> 02:08.221
about your own interests,

02:08.541 --> 02:09.261
fine.

02:10.180 --> 02:12.101
Whether Yan Studio thrives or fails

02:12.341 --> 02:12.981
will no longer

02:13.140 --> 02:13.981
concern you.

02:16.541 --> 02:17.981
I'll give you one minute to decide.

02:19.661 --> 02:21.221
If you decide to keep working with me,

02:21.700 --> 02:22.781
then go back.

02:24.061 --> 02:25.700
And I'll process final payments

02:26.180 --> 02:27.300
according to contract terms.

02:28.261 --> 02:29.821
If you decide not to,

02:30.460 --> 02:31.580
I'll pay you right now.

02:43.300 --> 02:43.821
Yan.

02:44.140 --> 02:45.020
Look who's here.

02:48.140 --> 02:48.781
Yan.

02:49.140 --> 02:49.981
Long time no see.

02:54.101 --> 02:54.981
What brings you here?

02:55.020 --> 02:55.860
Sweetie.

02:57.341 --> 02:58.341
I am

02:58.381 --> 02:59.700
representing Moscow

02:59.700 --> 03:02.180
for a Sino-Russian cultural exchange.

03:02.941 --> 03:04.700
I absolutely adore Yan Studio's dresses.

03:04.740 --> 03:05.541
So,

03:05.661 --> 03:06.941
I came to visit.

03:07.221 --> 03:07.860
Of course,

03:08.101 --> 03:09.381
I came mainly to see you.

03:11.781 --> 03:13.261
It's an honor to have you.

03:17.900 --> 03:19.501
Who are they?

03:21.620 --> 03:22.661
They are

03:23.501 --> 03:24.460
my partners.

03:24.900 --> 03:25.781
Hello.

03:26.781 --> 03:28.020
I must say

03:28.061 --> 03:30.180
you've shown excellent judgment

03:30.580 --> 03:32.580
in choosing to collaborate

03:32.661 --> 03:33.620
with a sophisticated

03:33.700 --> 03:35.341
and visionary brand.

03:36.061 --> 03:36.620
Thanks.

03:36.821 --> 03:38.180
We're very visionary.

03:38.620 --> 03:39.140
Exactly.

03:39.261 --> 03:39.860
Visionary.

03:39.981 --> 03:40.781
Visionary.

03:41.860 --> 03:42.981
You know what?

03:43.261 --> 03:44.740
In Russia now,

03:44.781 --> 03:46.460
Chinese-inspired dresses

03:46.460 --> 03:48.381
are considered the new trend.

03:48.860 --> 03:51.221
Is international expansion

03:51.261 --> 03:52.740
part of Yan Studio's

03:52.781 --> 03:54.061
development plans?

03:54.580 --> 03:55.541
Let me know

03:55.541 --> 03:56.501
if I can help.

03:58.661 --> 03:59.101
By the way,

03:59.300 --> 04:00.341
I need

04:00.341 --> 04:02.700
to attend a high-end closing banquet.

04:03.180 --> 04:05.541
Must choose a gown from Yan Studio.

04:06.061 --> 04:06.740
Help me pick one?

04:06.740 --> 04:07.341
No problem.

04:08.020 --> 04:10.020
Our new collection's ready.

04:10.501 --> 04:11.381
Let me show you.

04:21.060 --> 04:21.541
Hey.

04:22.260 --> 04:22.901
Leave it to me.

04:23.661 --> 04:24.180
Okay.

04:29.661 --> 04:30.141
Hi.

04:31.260 --> 04:32.300
Mr. Shen, right?

04:32.781 --> 04:33.541
Nice to meet you.

04:34.380 --> 04:34.820
Sit.

04:36.420 --> 04:37.781
We've long admired you.

04:38.141 --> 04:39.380
Your father and you

04:39.420 --> 04:40.541
are role models

04:40.620 --> 04:41.740
for all entrepreneurs.

04:42.221 --> 04:42.661
Indeed.

04:42.740 --> 04:43.420
Today,

04:43.541 --> 04:44.701
it's a pleasure

04:44.820 --> 04:46.420
to meet you.

04:47.221 --> 04:47.901
Yes, absolutely.

04:48.420 --> 04:48.901
Me too.

04:49.260 --> 04:49.781
Mr. Shen.

04:50.500 --> 04:51.620
Who is

04:51.860 --> 04:52.940
that lady?

04:54.180 --> 04:55.781
She's the wife

04:55.860 --> 04:57.901
of a Russian real estate tycoon,

04:58.300 --> 04:59.940
and Ms. Xu's close friend.

04:59.981 --> 05:01.461
She trusts this studio's potential.

05:01.541 --> 05:03.021
Perhaps Yan Studio will

05:03.101 --> 05:05.581
become an officially recognized company

05:05.620 --> 05:07.221
for cultural promotion.

05:08.101 --> 05:09.180
Orders will flood in.

05:10.021 --> 05:11.141
It's true?

05:14.180 --> 05:15.856
It's not easy
for my wife to do business.

05:16.221 --> 05:17.264
Please look out for her.

05:18.021 --> 05:19.541
No problem.

05:19.781 --> 05:21.221
We're all loyal partners

05:21.701 --> 05:22.940
of Yan Studio.

05:23.740 --> 05:24.781
Mr. Shen.

05:25.541 --> 05:26.341
Today,

05:26.500 --> 05:27.500
I promise you.

05:28.380 --> 05:29.461
Ms. Xu's business

05:29.901 --> 05:30.661
is ours.

05:30.701 --> 05:31.541
You can count on us.

05:33.141 --> 05:33.781
Thank you.

05:35.541 --> 05:36.141
Yan.

05:37.701 --> 05:38.221
Look!

05:38.260 --> 05:39.221
Is it pretty?

05:40.620 --> 05:41.461
I absolutely

05:41.461 --> 05:42.820
adore the dress you picked for me.

05:42.820 --> 05:43.901
It's perfect!

05:44.021 --> 05:44.820
So beautiful!

05:46.180 --> 05:47.141
Truly stunning!

05:48.860 --> 05:49.341
Yan,

05:50.380 --> 05:51.901
are you in some kind of trouble?

05:53.060 --> 05:53.701
No.

05:54.500 --> 05:56.101
Your husband told me everything.

05:58.180 --> 05:59.060
I believe

05:59.260 --> 06:00.820
you'll push through this darkness

06:01.060 --> 06:02.021
and see your rainbow.

06:02.781 --> 06:04.260
At Yanbo Resort,

06:04.581 --> 06:06.820
I saw your passion for your career.

06:07.420 --> 06:08.620
Any challenge

06:09.060 --> 06:10.260
won't defeat you.

06:18.860 --> 06:20.620
Those are the most empowering

06:22.740 --> 06:23.541
and comforting words

06:24.260 --> 06:25.541
I've heard recently.

06:28.300 --> 06:29.221
You can do this.

06:29.380 --> 06:30.260
Rest assured,

06:31.901 --> 06:32.860
I'll do my best

06:32.901 --> 06:33.904
to overcome the crisis.

06:34.860 --> 06:36.260
I'll keep wearing your designs

06:36.300 --> 06:37.820
and show them to the world.

06:40.060 --> 06:41.141
How long will you stay

06:41.221 --> 06:42.021
in Jingzhou?

06:43.060 --> 06:44.940
I came with my husband.

06:45.260 --> 06:46.300
He is here

06:46.300 --> 06:47.860
for a cross-border collaboration.

06:48.060 --> 06:48.620
For business?

06:49.021 --> 06:50.541
So, we do our things separately.

06:51.420 --> 06:51.860
By the way,

06:52.420 --> 06:53.300
your husband's company

06:53.300 --> 06:54.541
has been shortlisted

06:54.541 --> 06:55.420
for a partnership.

06:55.661 --> 06:57.420
But all candidates undergo

06:57.420 --> 06:58.740
a three-month evaluation period.

07:00.820 --> 07:02.860
I'll await good news in three months.

07:04.901 --> 07:06.541
During the evaluation period,

07:06.541 --> 07:07.860
you must come see me.

07:08.141 --> 07:09.581
I definitely will!

07:11.141 --> 07:12.141
Open your arms.

07:15.221 --> 07:17.820
Get precise measurements taken.

07:18.021 --> 07:18.701
Again?

07:18.781 --> 07:19.500
Of course!

07:19.541 --> 07:20.500
Then you can choose

07:20.500 --> 07:21.740
plenty of styles that suit you.

07:21.740 --> 07:23.101
Sounds great!

07:25.620 --> 07:26.860
Good luck.

07:27.461 --> 07:27.981
Goodbye.

07:28.461 --> 07:28.981
Goodbye.

07:42.581 --> 07:43.420
Thank you for today.

07:46.820 --> 07:47.981
I've heard

07:48.341 --> 07:49.141
of your situation.

07:50.420 --> 07:51.620
I keep watching you online.

07:54.180 --> 07:54.781
What?

07:55.180 --> 07:56.221
Want to lend me money?

07:59.581 --> 08:01.060
I won't undermine your principles

08:01.060 --> 08:01.820
or resolutions.

08:03.060 --> 08:04.221
But I must do something.

08:07.060 --> 08:08.420
Hear me out first.

08:08.901 --> 08:09.620
Look at this.

08:10.661 --> 08:12.420
This could help get your company

08:12.500 --> 08:13.300
out of crisis.

08:16.740 --> 08:19.141
Qinglan Cup Fashion Design Competition?

08:20.901 --> 08:22.581
Yao mentioned this before.

08:23.740 --> 08:25.060
It's highly influential

08:25.260 --> 08:26.940
in the design community.

08:29.101 --> 08:30.661
Major media outlets

08:31.101 --> 08:32.341
will cover it too.

08:32.821 --> 08:34.660
Winning this competition would

08:34.740 --> 08:35.500
help you

08:36.221 --> 08:37.101
gain recognition

08:37.140 --> 08:38.260
from the fashion industry.

08:39.181 --> 08:40.221
With an award, you will

08:40.620 --> 08:41.660
have a chance to speak,

08:42.301 --> 08:43.061
show people

08:43.181 --> 08:44.780
the authentic brocade,

08:45.581 --> 08:47.260
and restate Yan Studio's philosophy.

08:47.941 --> 08:48.821
You can tell consumers

08:49.380 --> 08:51.260
that intangible heritage stuff
is not priceless

08:51.860 --> 08:52.941
but worthwhile.

08:56.140 --> 08:57.740
Registration has closed already.

08:58.941 --> 09:00.221
I've already signed you up.

09:01.140 --> 09:02.821
Just submit the company documents
on time,

09:02.900 --> 09:03.981
along with the photos.

09:06.421 --> 09:08.301
Am I crossing the line?

09:12.941 --> 09:14.061
Thank you.

09:18.221 --> 09:19.181
I really

09:20.740 --> 09:21.461
appreciate it.

09:23.660 --> 09:24.821
I won't disturb you.

09:25.701 --> 09:26.380
I'm leaving.

09:26.891 --> 09:29.148
♪As lucky as we are♪

09:29.213 --> 09:31.293
♪Two passionate hearts are♪

09:31.760 --> 09:34.160
♪In perfect harmony♪

09:34.448 --> 09:36.496
♪Since the day I met you♪

09:36.592 --> 09:39.008
♪I've been looking forward to each trip♪

09:39.183 --> 09:41.616
♪We can go anywhere♪

09:41.712 --> 09:44.464
♪With you by my side♪

09:44.464 --> 09:48.592
♪Rain or shine♪

09:48.592 --> 09:52.304
♪I'm here with you♪

10:01.780 --> 10:03.020
Starting today, we'll split

10:03.260 --> 10:04.181
into two groups.

10:04.380 --> 10:05.701
Meng Zhao and Huanhuan will

10:05.701 --> 10:07.181
handle the sales of the second batch.

10:07.301 --> 10:08.020
Everyone else

10:08.061 --> 10:09.101
will fully help Yao

10:09.101 --> 10:10.821
with the Qinglan Cup competition.

10:10.981 --> 10:11.421
Good luck!

10:11.581 --> 10:12.341
I hope

10:12.380 --> 10:13.740
you can do your best.

10:13.981 --> 10:15.421
Now, let's have Yao explain

10:15.421 --> 10:17.221
the concept behind
our competition entries.

10:17.660 --> 10:19.260
For this collection,

10:19.260 --> 10:20.461
I'm planning

10:20.461 --> 10:21.900
to use traditional handmade fabrics.

10:22.020 --> 10:23.301
The fabrics

10:23.301 --> 10:25.380
require Su embroidery techniques.

10:25.540 --> 10:26.421
These three

10:26.421 --> 10:28.380
are my preliminary designs.

10:28.540 --> 10:29.301
The first piece,

10:29.301 --> 10:30.900
titled Flames,

10:30.941 --> 10:32.821
uses white

10:32.941 --> 10:34.860
and red hues

10:34.860 --> 10:36.181
to make a great contrast,

10:36.701 --> 10:38.260
expressing both elegance

10:38.260 --> 10:39.540
and attraction.

10:39.620 --> 10:41.101
The second one...

10:41.140 --> 10:41.900
We need photographs

10:41.900 --> 10:42.981
showing front,

10:42.981 --> 10:43.981
back,

10:44.380 --> 10:45.260
and side profiles

10:45.260 --> 10:46.981
of each garment.

10:47.380 --> 10:48.821
Ensure structural

10:48.821 --> 10:50.020
and design integrity,

10:50.101 --> 10:51.140
and complete accessories.

10:51.701 --> 10:52.860
Through detailed close-ups,

10:52.900 --> 10:54.101
we must highlight the quality

10:54.140 --> 10:55.461
and texture of the fabrics

10:55.740 --> 10:57.181
and the fancy hand craftsmanship.

10:57.181 --> 10:59.024
♪Cut off malicious labels♪

11:00.461 --> 11:03.620
What do you think?

11:05.040 --> 11:06.544
♪Perfect, for no one♪

11:06.832 --> 11:08.541
♪I got reborn♪

11:08.620 --> 11:09.461
Very good!

11:10.660 --> 11:12.181
You've well mixed traditional fashion

11:12.701 --> 11:13.821
with modern one.

11:15.380 --> 11:17.061
The detailing is impeccable.

11:17.181 --> 11:18.660
This is true artisanal craftsmanship.

11:19.780 --> 11:20.780
Yao, you know what?

11:21.101 --> 11:22.301
My proudest achievement

11:22.540 --> 11:23.981
is being your permanent model.

11:26.011 --> 11:27.530
♪Discard what doesn't fit♪

11:27.581 --> 11:28.500
What's wrong?

11:28.540 --> 11:29.981
Why are you crying?

11:33.101 --> 11:35.140
The stress just got to me.

11:35.780 --> 11:36.620
Cry if you want to.

11:36.860 --> 11:38.140
Let it all out.

11:38.860 --> 11:39.421
Look,

11:40.221 --> 11:41.780
my shoulders are yours.

11:43.260 --> 11:44.341
Get out of here!

11:44.380 --> 11:45.140
Come on.

11:45.260 --> 11:46.941
I'm just emotional

11:47.140 --> 11:48.421
because of my beautiful designs.

11:49.101 --> 11:50.020
Unbelievable!

11:50.020 --> 11:51.701
Who designed this masterpiece?

11:51.740 --> 11:53.740
It's breathtaking!

11:54.780 --> 11:56.140
Stop it.

11:57.221 --> 11:58.301
Then Qiao Lin and I...

11:58.500 --> 12:00.540
Can I lean on you, Yan?

12:01.260 --> 12:02.301
I'll go try the outfit.

12:02.540 --> 12:03.380
Wait a moment.

12:03.660 --> 12:04.941
I'm coming with you.

12:05.020 --> 12:05.941
Me too.

12:06.140 --> 12:07.701
Don't ruin my clothes.

12:09.488 --> 12:11.120
♪Every frame's perfection♪

12:11.376 --> 12:17.296
♪My beauty's defined by none
but my own command♪

12:17.296 --> 12:20.112
♪Ready to shine♪

12:21.874 --> 12:25.264
♪Ready to shine♪

12:25.648 --> 12:27.728
♪Ready to shine♪

12:29.168 --> 12:30.672
♪Ready to shine♪

12:40.860 --> 12:41.540
Ms. Xu.

12:42.061 --> 12:43.900
I noticed an accounting irregularity

12:44.260 --> 12:46.301
while processing payments.

12:46.981 --> 12:47.620
Take a look.

12:50.701 --> 12:51.821
This situation

12:51.900 --> 12:53.221
is completely new to me.

12:53.620 --> 12:55.380
I usually just

12:55.461 --> 12:56.341
assist Mr. Dong,

12:56.780 --> 12:57.540
so I'm unfamiliar

12:57.540 --> 12:58.740
with the remaining procedures.

12:58.780 --> 13:00.101
I have no idea

13:00.101 --> 13:01.020
how to fix this.

13:01.860 --> 13:02.941
Tried to reach Dong?

13:03.380 --> 13:04.301
Sure.

13:04.860 --> 13:06.260
But his phone's disconnected.

13:06.500 --> 13:07.740
His WeChat account is deleted.

13:08.101 --> 13:08.900
He has

13:08.900 --> 13:10.421
crossed the line!

13:10.500 --> 13:11.941
He doesn't want us to find him.

13:11.941 --> 13:13.020
He's running away.

13:15.312 --> 13:17.584
(Sold a batch of clothing,
processing fee)

13:18.101 --> 13:20.140
Mr. Lin once collaborated

13:20.181 --> 13:22.020
with Mr. Dong

13:22.140 --> 13:22.900
on work.

13:23.260 --> 13:25.061
He seemed professional

13:25.821 --> 13:27.341
and checked the accounting quickly.

13:27.660 --> 13:28.620
Why don't we

13:29.020 --> 13:29.900
ask him for help?

13:30.461 --> 13:31.020
I see.

13:31.301 --> 13:31.941
You may leave.

13:32.260 --> 13:32.900
Alright, Ms. Xu.

13:33.101 --> 13:33.860
I'll go back.

13:46.020 --> 13:46.620
Yan.

13:48.421 --> 13:49.301
Good idea.

13:50.341 --> 13:50.821
Can we talk?

13:51.380 --> 13:51.941
Sure.

13:54.101 --> 13:55.061
Here is the thing.

13:56.101 --> 13:56.860
You know

13:57.101 --> 13:58.821
we've been struggling to hire a CFO.

13:59.341 --> 14:00.341
The accounting assistant

14:00.341 --> 14:01.260
has been overwhelmed.

14:01.740 --> 14:02.821
So she asked me

14:03.101 --> 14:03.941
if it's possible

14:04.701 --> 14:07.181
to have Lin Tao temporarily
fill the position.

14:08.740 --> 14:09.301
Lin Tao?

14:09.341 --> 14:09.981
It's fine.

14:10.061 --> 14:11.301
If you have a problem,

14:11.900 --> 14:12.701
we could actually

14:12.701 --> 14:13.701
wait a bit longer.

14:13.900 --> 14:14.941
We'll hire someone anyway.

14:15.740 --> 14:16.821
No problem. I don't object.

14:17.540 --> 14:19.181
We can't
leave a finance position vacant.

14:19.701 --> 14:20.500
It's for business.

14:23.740 --> 14:25.140
Are you concerned about...?

14:25.780 --> 14:27.061
No, I'm not worried.

14:27.421 --> 14:28.860
Lin Tao happens to be unemployed.

14:28.860 --> 14:30.301
He's got nothing to do.

14:30.581 --> 14:31.581
This position actually

14:31.900 --> 14:32.821
suits him well.

14:33.061 --> 14:33.701
I'll explain

14:33.701 --> 14:34.701
to Yu Yiming.

14:34.740 --> 14:35.500
Don't worry.

14:36.101 --> 14:36.981
Is it really okay?

14:37.221 --> 14:37.740
Sure.

14:39.900 --> 14:40.301
Okay.

14:40.660 --> 14:41.620
Then it's settled.

14:41.941 --> 14:42.500
I'm leaving.

14:47.568 --> 14:48.421
(Payment Reminder:
Please settle balance promptly)

14:48.421 --> 14:49.301
(Sender: Ruibo Fabric Company)
This was received

14:49.301 --> 14:50.581
yesterday.

14:50.900 --> 14:52.581
This wasn't

14:52.581 --> 14:53.620
filed before.

14:53.821 --> 14:54.701
Mr. Dong

14:54.701 --> 14:55.860
handled this personally.

14:55.900 --> 14:57.941
I was completely unaware of it.

14:58.341 --> 14:59.301
Now,

14:59.341 --> 15:00.500
he's completely disappeared

15:00.540 --> 15:01.701
and can't be found.

15:03.900 --> 15:04.461
Don't worry.

15:05.620 --> 15:09.740
Ruibo Fabric Company?

15:12.140 --> 15:12.860
Liu.

15:13.341 --> 15:14.500
I remember

15:14.540 --> 15:15.581
during our last session,

15:15.821 --> 15:17.020
there was a receipt

15:17.301 --> 15:19.020
from the same company.

15:19.780 --> 15:21.620
Gather all financial records

15:21.620 --> 15:22.860
of the company.

15:23.301 --> 15:24.181
Let's recheck them.

15:24.421 --> 15:25.780
Okay, I'll retrieve them.

15:26.620 --> 15:27.380
All here.

15:30.500 --> 15:31.181
Mr. Lin.

15:31.500 --> 15:32.581
I owe you.

15:32.581 --> 15:33.860
Thank you so much.

15:34.061 --> 15:34.821
You actually

15:34.821 --> 15:36.221
remember a receipt.

15:36.660 --> 15:38.101
Unexpectedly, it led us to uncover

15:38.101 --> 15:39.101
such a substantial sum.

15:40.061 --> 15:40.620
No problem.

15:40.900 --> 15:42.421
If you have any problems, let me know.

15:42.860 --> 15:44.020
Finance work is always

15:44.301 --> 15:44.941
detail-oriented.

15:45.181 --> 15:46.221
Every detail matters

15:46.260 --> 15:47.101
immensely.

15:47.221 --> 15:47.780
Understood.

15:49.740 --> 15:50.181
Ms. Xu.

15:50.421 --> 15:51.380
It's all settled.

15:51.900 --> 15:52.740
All thanks to

15:52.740 --> 15:53.941
Mr. Lin's assistance today.

15:55.620 --> 15:56.181
Thank you.

15:56.900 --> 15:57.581
Liu,

15:57.981 --> 15:58.620
you may leave.

15:58.860 --> 15:59.941
I'll get back to work.

16:02.020 --> 16:02.540
Lin Tao.

16:02.900 --> 16:04.020
It's time to have lunch.

16:04.101 --> 16:05.500
Join us for lunch?

16:05.821 --> 16:06.701
I'll pass.

16:06.900 --> 16:08.221
I'm glad I could help.

16:08.461 --> 16:09.301
See you.

16:09.780 --> 16:10.260
Lin Tao.

16:12.101 --> 16:13.341
Qiao Lin told me

16:13.780 --> 16:14.701
about your situation.

16:15.701 --> 16:17.301
Where are you working?

16:19.380 --> 16:20.461
At the martial arts gym.

16:20.981 --> 16:21.821
Doing odd jobs.

16:22.421 --> 16:23.140
Just let me know

16:23.140 --> 16:24.701
if you have financial matters.

16:25.500 --> 16:27.540
I can be your external consultant.

16:29.301 --> 16:29.981
Here's the thing.

16:31.540 --> 16:32.900
Since our CFO

16:32.900 --> 16:33.821
left his position,

16:34.701 --> 16:36.260
the role has been vacant.

16:37.740 --> 16:38.701
So,

16:39.701 --> 16:41.780
if you want to change your job,

16:42.620 --> 16:43.540
you can join us.

16:46.780 --> 16:47.260
Me?

16:48.620 --> 16:49.380
Is that okay?

16:49.620 --> 16:50.540
Absolutely.

16:52.140 --> 16:54.341
You understand my company's finances

16:54.740 --> 16:56.101
and have professional skills.

16:56.301 --> 16:58.221
Even Liu admires you.

16:59.780 --> 17:01.221
But for the record,

17:01.821 --> 17:03.600
there's a three-month probation period.

17:04.221 --> 17:05.020
If it's okay,

17:05.020 --> 17:06.100
you can start tomorrow.

17:07.060 --> 17:08.100
Of course.

17:08.461 --> 17:09.381
To be honest,

17:10.141 --> 17:11.060
Qiao Lin knows

17:11.740 --> 17:13.500
I lost my banking job.

17:14.500 --> 17:16.020
I don't want to return home

17:16.020 --> 17:17.008
and upset my parents.

17:17.260 --> 17:18.540
I wanted to stay in Jingzhou

17:18.580 --> 17:19.580
and find a new job

17:19.621 --> 17:20.461
before telling them.

17:20.661 --> 17:22.221
I don't want them to worry about me.

17:23.221 --> 17:24.020
You should

17:24.020 --> 17:24.941
call them later

17:24.981 --> 17:25.701
and reassure them.

17:26.701 --> 17:28.060
Welcome aboard.

17:29.340 --> 17:30.020
Welcome.

17:31.621 --> 17:33.020
Thank you for trusting me.

17:33.461 --> 17:34.421
I will

17:34.461 --> 17:35.500
do a good job,

17:35.981 --> 17:37.381
so you can focus on business

17:37.621 --> 17:39.100
without worries.

17:40.260 --> 17:40.981
See you tomorrow.

17:41.661 --> 17:42.141
Okay.

17:42.221 --> 17:43.340
I'll go get prepared.

17:52.701 --> 17:53.820
Let's get back

17:53.861 --> 17:54.780
to where we were.

17:56.340 --> 17:58.260
When pairing with silver accessories,

17:58.300 --> 17:59.300
use black eyeshadow.

17:59.381 --> 17:59.820
Yan.

18:00.500 --> 18:01.020
Yes?

18:01.861 --> 18:02.740
Our eligibility

18:02.740 --> 18:03.621
for the competition

18:03.621 --> 18:04.340
was revoked.

18:05.008 --> 18:05.904
(We regret to inform you of your disqualification
from the Qinglan Cup competition.)

18:12.100 --> 18:13.381
Stop wasting your time here.

18:13.820 --> 18:14.621
It's pointless.

18:15.340 --> 18:16.981
Getting Yan Studio requalified

18:16.981 --> 18:18.141
isn't within my authority.

18:20.340 --> 18:21.340
Can you help us

18:21.340 --> 18:22.020
contact

18:22.340 --> 18:23.381
the person in charge?

18:23.540 --> 18:24.020
We can

18:24.020 --> 18:25.181
explain it again

18:25.461 --> 18:26.941
in detail.

18:27.181 --> 18:27.941
I assure you

18:28.141 --> 18:29.100
our clothing quality

18:29.100 --> 18:30.260
is impeccable.

18:31.141 --> 18:31.861
You've explained

18:31.861 --> 18:32.621
clearly enough,

18:32.941 --> 18:33.941
but the point is,

18:33.941 --> 18:35.740
explanations aren't enough.

18:36.381 --> 18:37.141
A contestant

18:37.141 --> 18:38.381
with ongoing public disputes

18:38.381 --> 18:39.100
would negatively

18:39.100 --> 18:40.421
controversial our competition.

18:40.941 --> 18:42.060
But we're clearly

18:42.100 --> 18:43.500
the victims of counterfeits!

18:43.540 --> 18:45.100
How does that make us guilty?

18:45.421 --> 18:45.981
Miss.

18:46.181 --> 18:48.020
We've tried our best

18:48.260 --> 18:49.941
to mitigate the negative impact.

18:49.941 --> 18:51.300
- So...
- But the rumors persist!

18:52.260 --> 18:53.181
It's provoked gossip,

18:53.181 --> 18:54.020
true or not.

18:54.181 --> 18:55.221
Please leave now.

18:55.941 --> 18:56.381
Miss.

18:56.500 --> 18:57.020
Wait.

18:57.461 --> 18:58.181
Please consider.

18:58.381 --> 18:59.381
Yan Studio

18:59.381 --> 19:00.780
values cultural heritage.

19:00.820 --> 19:01.621
We use

19:01.621 --> 19:02.901
handwoven brocade.

19:02.981 --> 19:03.740
The counterfeits

19:03.740 --> 19:04.740
are machine-made.

19:04.740 --> 19:06.100
You should investigate it!

19:06.260 --> 19:07.701
Why aren't you investigating?

19:09.020 --> 19:09.701
Miss.

19:10.981 --> 19:11.981
Miss, here's the thing.

19:12.540 --> 19:13.981
The reason we persist so strongly

19:13.981 --> 19:15.100
in joining this competition

19:15.100 --> 19:16.901
is to seize this chance
to help the public

19:17.461 --> 19:18.820
distinguish right from wrong.

19:19.300 --> 19:21.461
This isn't just
about clearing Yan Studio's name

19:21.584 --> 19:23.901
but also showing respect
for intangible cultural heritage.

19:23.901 --> 19:24.701
What do you say?

19:24.941 --> 19:25.701
Clearing your name

19:25.701 --> 19:27.300
isn't the organizer's obligation.

19:28.100 --> 19:29.661
I've made my position clear.

19:29.981 --> 19:30.740
I can't

19:30.740 --> 19:31.580
help you.

19:31.780 --> 19:32.981
Instead of wasting time here,

19:32.981 --> 19:34.461
you should focus on damage control.

19:34.820 --> 19:36.221
Removing your stains matters.

19:38.100 --> 19:38.580
Chen.

19:39.421 --> 19:39.820
Come.

19:39.941 --> 19:40.621
The fifth group.

19:51.941 --> 19:53.540
Are we really leaving like this?

19:53.820 --> 19:54.780
We should stay here

19:54.820 --> 19:56.181
until they give us approval.

19:57.020 --> 19:58.141
She said we have stains?

19:58.621 --> 19:59.861
What kind of organizer is that?

19:59.901 --> 20:00.941
With zero accountability.

20:01.300 --> 20:02.768
Always dodging responsibility.

20:06.300 --> 20:07.421
Let's try something else.

20:09.181 --> 20:10.448
We must join the competition.

20:25.621 --> 20:26.661
(Qiao Lin)
Yan Studio has been disqualified

20:26.661 --> 20:27.461
for the competition

20:27.461 --> 20:28.820
and thinks we would

20:28.861 --> 20:30.500
negatively impact the competition.

20:35.661 --> 20:36.221
Mr. Shen.

20:37.580 --> 20:38.300
Sun Siwei is here.

20:38.780 --> 20:40.020
She wants to interview you.

20:41.181 --> 20:42.141
Haven't I already

20:42.141 --> 20:42.740
declined?

20:42.941 --> 20:43.340
Fine.

20:43.661 --> 20:44.421
I'll send her away.

20:45.981 --> 20:46.421
Wait.

20:50.500 --> 20:51.300
Have her get ready.

20:52.580 --> 20:53.260
This is

20:53.260 --> 20:54.300
an update on the progress

20:54.421 --> 20:55.580
of the New District project.

20:55.780 --> 20:56.181
Good.

20:56.500 --> 20:57.941
Thank you

20:57.941 --> 20:58.981
for this interview.

20:59.421 --> 21:00.461
We know you are

21:00.461 --> 21:01.421
typically low-profile

21:01.461 --> 21:03.100
and rarely appear

21:03.141 --> 21:04.020
in the spotlight.

21:04.221 --> 21:05.381
Making an exception today

21:05.381 --> 21:06.300
to be interviewed by me

21:06.300 --> 21:07.221
is my honor.

21:08.060 --> 21:09.300
Don't overinterpret this.

21:09.740 --> 21:11.661
I'm not making exceptions for anyone.

21:13.100 --> 21:15.221
My wife founded Yan Studio

21:15.300 --> 21:16.621
and faced some complications.

21:17.981 --> 21:19.100
I learn

21:19.661 --> 21:21.861
that keeping low-key is good.

21:22.540 --> 21:24.020
But if overdone,

21:24.260 --> 21:26.780
it will be bad.

21:27.300 --> 21:29.181
It makes others overlook

21:29.381 --> 21:30.340
your strengths.

21:31.221 --> 21:33.540
My wife originally wanted

21:33.621 --> 21:34.941
to work quietly.

21:34.941 --> 21:36.661
She stopped me

21:36.780 --> 21:37.820
from promoting her brand.

21:38.381 --> 21:40.340
But in the end,

21:41.181 --> 21:42.461
some people maliciously

21:42.820 --> 21:43.901
created knockoffs,

21:43.941 --> 21:45.060
tarnishing her reputation.

21:46.221 --> 21:48.060
Yet numerous influencers

21:48.100 --> 21:49.580
conducted comparisons

21:49.621 --> 21:51.100
between Yan Studio's clothes

21:51.141 --> 21:52.461
and the counterfeits.

21:52.621 --> 21:54.500
Their conclusion showed

21:54.540 --> 21:55.580
no big differences.

21:55.580 --> 21:56.100
Perhaps

21:56.340 --> 21:57.300
the only difference is

21:57.300 --> 21:58.661
that Yan Studio charges more.

21:59.100 --> 22:00.060
Many consumers

22:00.060 --> 22:01.260
felt outraged

22:01.260 --> 22:03.381
by the result,

22:03.461 --> 22:03.941
accusing

22:04.141 --> 22:05.100
Yan Studio

22:05.100 --> 22:06.861
of treating customers as fools.

22:07.540 --> 22:08.901
What's your response, Mr. Shen?

22:10.340 --> 22:11.221
As everyone knows,

22:11.820 --> 22:13.740
Jinda Group's properties

22:14.100 --> 22:15.580
never compete through price wars.

22:16.941 --> 22:19.181
Our construction philosophy ensures

22:19.421 --> 22:20.981
every brick,

22:21.701 --> 22:23.020
or every steel beam,

22:23.580 --> 22:25.181
or even every grain of sand

22:25.421 --> 22:26.981
meets national standards.

22:27.421 --> 22:28.500
It's not

22:29.260 --> 22:30.740
about appearance.

22:31.540 --> 22:33.540
After enduring a storm,

22:33.540 --> 22:35.020
property owners will know

22:35.020 --> 22:35.981
what it means

22:36.461 --> 22:37.461
to get what they pay for.

22:38.580 --> 22:39.901
Just like Yan Studio,

22:40.300 --> 22:43.340
they insist on using handwoven brocade,

22:43.941 --> 22:45.941
aiming to convey cultural values

22:46.020 --> 22:47.901
embedded in the craftsmanship.

22:48.540 --> 22:49.981
Some attention-seeking influencers

22:50.020 --> 22:51.181
distort facts and claim

22:51.260 --> 22:52.221
that my wife

22:53.181 --> 22:54.861
is exploiting nostalgia for profit

22:55.861 --> 22:57.020
and deceiving consumers.

22:57.500 --> 22:58.701
That is nonsense.

23:00.300 --> 23:02.461
May I ask if your statement

23:02.580 --> 23:03.780
represents Jinda's position?

23:03.820 --> 23:05.141
Or is this a personal endorsement

23:05.141 --> 23:06.500
for Yan Studio?

23:07.500 --> 23:08.901
The public should

23:08.901 --> 23:09.540
listen to

23:09.540 --> 23:11.020
Yan Studio.

23:12.621 --> 23:13.941
Certain malicious individuals

23:14.060 --> 23:15.020
disregarded truths

23:15.540 --> 23:16.661
for attention.

23:17.300 --> 23:18.780
They created the buzz

23:18.861 --> 23:20.820
to tarnish Yan Studio's reputation.

23:22.060 --> 23:22.941
This is cyberbullying,

23:24.221 --> 23:24.941
not justice.

23:26.820 --> 23:27.260
Understood.

23:28.060 --> 23:29.780
As a spouse,

23:29.941 --> 23:32.100
what advice would you give

23:32.141 --> 23:33.340
your entrepreneurial wife?

23:34.300 --> 23:35.901
Her vision remains

23:35.901 --> 23:36.820
remarkably clear.

23:36.901 --> 23:37.461
Therefore,

23:37.740 --> 23:39.421
she requires no suggestions from me.

23:39.981 --> 23:41.461
Instead, I should learn

23:41.461 --> 23:42.540
about her perseverance

23:43.260 --> 23:44.100
and composure.

23:46.580 --> 23:48.500
In this fast-paced world,

23:48.901 --> 23:51.221
my wife deliberately chose

23:51.221 --> 23:52.861
labor-intensive handmade textiles.

23:53.381 --> 23:54.381
(She knew)

23:54.381 --> 23:55.461
(this path would be tough.)

23:56.221 --> 23:57.981
(Yet she leads her team)

23:58.540 --> 23:59.661
(into rural villages,)

24:00.780 --> 24:01.901
(realizing production)

24:01.981 --> 24:03.221
(of the embroidery,)

24:04.381 --> 24:05.621
(and giving local women)

24:05.820 --> 24:06.941
(many jobs to do.)

24:07.580 --> 24:09.020
(Their husbands working outside)

24:09.500 --> 24:10.500
(may return home)

24:11.181 --> 24:12.500
(and live with their families)

24:12.901 --> 24:14.181
(and children.)

24:14.820 --> 24:16.300
(Children won't be left behind.)

24:17.100 --> 24:18.300
(My wife is)

24:18.300 --> 24:19.421
(doing a meaningful career)

24:19.621 --> 24:21.181
(with compassion.)

24:23.861 --> 24:24.981
(She's my role model.)

24:26.020 --> 24:27.060
(I'm proud of her.)

24:27.293 --> 24:28.980
♪Feeling so lost and feeling♪

24:28.980 --> 24:30.489
♪So much distractions♪

24:30.736 --> 24:31.920
♪Never imagined♪

24:31.920 --> 24:33.584
♪You'd stay by my side♪

24:35.216 --> 24:36.848
♪Comforting my sorrows♪

24:39.024 --> 24:40.656
♪On the midnight streets♪

24:41.072 --> 24:42.256
♪In shadowed corners♪

24:42.256 --> 24:44.048
♪Remember that moment♪

24:44.518 --> 24:46.608
♪You smiled and looked at me♪

24:52.368 --> 24:54.224
♪At that moment, the world♪

24:54.224 --> 24:57.360
♪Just you and me♪

24:59.152 --> 25:01.068
♪Enjoying the city life♪

25:01.068 --> 25:04.848
♪Holding your hand♪

25:10.000 --> 25:11.376
(Live Stream Script)

25:11.780 --> 25:12.941
(Don't overinterpret this.)

25:13.340 --> 25:14.661
(I'm not...)

25:18.141 --> 25:18.861
Boss.

25:21.020 --> 25:22.060
Shen Haoming

25:22.381 --> 25:23.221
is pretty smart.

25:24.580 --> 25:26.941
He leveraged press coverage
to reverse public opinion

25:27.820 --> 25:29.141
while promoting himself

25:29.181 --> 25:30.621
as a good husband.

25:31.580 --> 25:33.141
He is quite shrewd.

25:36.780 --> 25:37.861
If Xu Yan knows

25:38.032 --> 25:39.701
about Baraikin's three-month probation

25:39.701 --> 25:41.060
for Shen Haoming,

25:43.221 --> 25:43.981
how

25:43.981 --> 25:44.981
will she

25:45.861 --> 25:46.901
perceive his actions?

25:47.060 --> 25:48.020
(My wife's pursuing...)

25:48.701 --> 25:49.260
Yan.

25:49.901 --> 25:50.901
Shen Haoming's interview

25:50.941 --> 25:52.221
defending Yan Studio

25:52.260 --> 25:52.861
went viral.

25:52.941 --> 25:53.621
I saw it.

25:54.020 --> 25:54.901
(I'm proud of her.)

25:55.060 --> 25:56.780
We have 500 more followers in an hour.

25:57.020 --> 25:58.421
The video traffic has spiked.

25:59.540 --> 26:00.461
We got more orders.

26:00.540 --> 26:01.661
Cancellations reversed.

26:02.181 --> 26:03.060
Mrs. Baraikin

26:03.060 --> 26:04.701
went to a party in a dress we designed.

26:04.780 --> 26:05.461
We're trending!

26:05.461 --> 26:06.381
Really?

26:07.340 --> 26:07.901
Let me see.

26:07.901 --> 26:08.461
Check it out.

26:12.780 --> 26:14.020
New supportive voices emerged!

26:14.260 --> 26:14.780
Listen.

26:14.864 --> 26:16.381
Important figures choose Yan Studio.

26:16.381 --> 26:17.540
True connoisseurs exist!

26:17.780 --> 26:18.780
Influencers can't

26:18.861 --> 26:19.981
appreciate the value

26:20.020 --> 26:21.020
of the genuine artistry.

26:29.100 --> 26:29.820
So we can't

26:29.820 --> 26:30.981
keep making compromises.

26:33.381 --> 26:35.141
We can also utilize
the power of social media

26:36.421 --> 26:39.020
to fight against those
scheming behind our backs,

26:40.981 --> 26:42.661
defend our rightful interests,

26:42.861 --> 26:44.340
and reclaim what's ours.

26:46.621 --> 26:47.780
(Live Stream Script)
This is the script.

26:48.861 --> 26:49.461
All of you,

26:50.141 --> 26:50.861
get ready.

26:55.060 --> 26:55.621
Hello, guys.

26:55.621 --> 26:57.421
I'm Guan, Yan Studio's streamer.

26:58.260 --> 26:59.141
Recently,

26:59.181 --> 27:00.820
Yan Studio has faced negative rumors.

27:00.820 --> 27:02.661
We didn't respond publicly

27:02.981 --> 27:04.861
to avoid falling into a trap.

27:05.181 --> 27:05.740
However,

27:05.941 --> 27:07.661
your supportive voices reached us.

27:07.941 --> 27:08.740
Now, it's time

27:08.981 --> 27:10.701
to show the real Yan Studio.

27:11.221 --> 27:11.820
Hello, guys.

27:12.300 --> 27:13.540
I'm Lu Baoyao, designer

27:13.540 --> 27:14.300
at Yan Studio.

27:15.421 --> 27:16.701
As a girl of the Yi people,

27:17.300 --> 27:19.060
(I grew up watching my grandma,)

27:19.100 --> 27:19.661
(mother,)

27:19.740 --> 27:21.260
(and villagers)

27:21.661 --> 27:23.300
(embroider and craft headwear.)

27:23.701 --> 27:24.861
(Yan Studio)
(In our tradition,)

27:25.100 --> 27:26.780
(from birth to adulthood,)

27:27.421 --> 27:28.701
(at every milestone,)

27:28.820 --> 27:30.020
(female elders collaborate)

27:30.060 --> 27:31.820
(to make exquisite attire for girls.)

27:32.221 --> 27:33.181
(Every stitch)

27:33.260 --> 27:34.661
(carries love and hope.)

27:35.621 --> 27:36.500
(Yan Studio)

27:37.020 --> 27:37.901
(helped)

27:38.100 --> 27:39.621
(fulfill my dream to share embroidery)

27:39.661 --> 27:40.861
(with the world.)

27:41.580 --> 27:42.461
(It transformed)

27:42.820 --> 27:44.340
(hidden folk crafts)

27:44.461 --> 27:45.300
(into commodities.)

27:45.381 --> 27:46.621
(Villagers have livelihoods.)

27:47.221 --> 27:47.820
(Yes.)

27:48.181 --> 27:48.861
(Look,)

27:48.861 --> 27:49.981
(our handwoven brocade)

27:49.981 --> 27:51.580
(is entrusted to three villages)

27:51.580 --> 27:52.340
(to maintain)

27:52.340 --> 27:54.901
(current production levels.)

27:55.060 --> 27:56.020
(Our quality)

27:56.141 --> 27:57.981
(totally differs from that)

27:57.981 --> 27:59.580
(of mass-produced knockoffs.)

27:59.740 --> 28:01.221
(Handcrafted textiles)

28:01.260 --> 28:03.060
(and tridimensional embroidery skills)

28:03.221 --> 28:05.141
(can only be fully appreciated)

28:05.221 --> 28:06.260
(through touch)

28:06.340 --> 28:07.300
(and wearing.)

28:07.500 --> 28:09.020
(They demand firsthand experience.)

28:09.981 --> 28:10.861
(Despite slander)

28:10.861 --> 28:13.060
(and doubt,)

28:13.141 --> 28:14.820
(we choose integrity,)

28:15.060 --> 28:16.740
(preserving intangible heritage)

28:16.780 --> 28:17.981
(through modern design.)

28:18.421 --> 28:19.340
(We aspire)

28:19.340 --> 28:20.181
(to show our work)

28:20.221 --> 28:22.340
(at the Qinglan Cup competition)

28:22.500 --> 28:23.461
(and make more people)

28:23.540 --> 28:25.540
(appreciate Yan Studio's clothes.)

28:26.141 --> 28:27.820
(Against those spreading lies,)

28:27.820 --> 28:29.461
(fueling baseless rumors,)

28:29.461 --> 28:30.661
(and smearing Yan Studio,)

28:30.661 --> 28:32.060
(Yan Studio Issues Official Statement!)
(we won't back down.)

28:32.340 --> 28:33.941
(We'll wield legal action)

28:34.060 --> 28:35.461
(to protect our rights.)

28:35.740 --> 28:36.740
In today's live stream,

28:36.820 --> 28:37.740
Yan Studio

28:37.740 --> 28:38.901
(declares a fight)

28:38.901 --> 28:40.580
(Support Authentic Brands!)
(against online malicious actors.)

28:41.020 --> 28:41.820
(Cyberbullying)

28:41.941 --> 28:42.740
(will)

28:42.740 --> 28:43.701
(meet an end.)

28:44.461 --> 28:45.060
(Say No to Knockoffs!)
(Moreover,)

28:45.141 --> 28:46.661
(Support Justice!)
(we need your backing)

28:46.780 --> 28:48.080
(to clear Yan Studio's name.)

29:00.340 --> 29:01.020
Hello?

29:01.340 --> 29:02.661
Is this Yan Studio?

29:04.141 --> 29:05.221
Yes, who is this?

29:06.580 --> 29:08.240
This is the organizer
of the Qinglan Cup.

29:09.300 --> 29:10.221
We have

29:10.221 --> 29:11.941
received many public requests

29:11.941 --> 29:13.941
to requalify Yan Studio

29:13.941 --> 29:15.300
for the competition.

29:15.941 --> 29:16.780
After deliberation,

29:16.901 --> 29:18.221
we decided

29:18.221 --> 29:19.300
to requalify Yan Studio.

29:23.780 --> 29:24.260
Thank you.

29:25.300 --> 29:26.701
When choosing partners,

29:27.181 --> 29:28.901
I value more than just business acumen.

29:29.661 --> 29:32.661
I also assess his character
and attitude towards family members.

29:33.060 --> 29:34.421
My wife mentioned

29:34.500 --> 29:36.100
Yan Studio has encountered difficulties.

29:36.661 --> 29:38.500
What impressed me was your approach.

29:38.941 --> 29:40.820
As a husband,
you silently supported your wife

29:41.500 --> 29:43.381
without overshadowing her brilliance.

29:43.701 --> 29:44.820
That's truly commendable.

29:45.901 --> 29:46.540
You flatter me.

29:48.181 --> 29:48.820
Actually,

29:49.500 --> 29:50.740
what made me decide

29:50.780 --> 29:52.421
to partner with Jinda Group

29:52.901 --> 29:54.100
was seeing how wisely

29:54.221 --> 29:55.820
you manage your marriage

29:56.941 --> 29:59.020
and your wife's relentless drive

29:59.141 --> 30:00.500
to succeed.

30:00.941 --> 30:01.580
Mr. Shen.

30:02.421 --> 30:04.020
After our interactions,

30:04.141 --> 30:05.861
I'm satisfied with Jinda's strength

30:05.941 --> 30:06.941
and sincerity.

30:08.421 --> 30:09.661
Jinda also highly values

30:09.820 --> 30:10.701
this collaboration.

30:11.941 --> 30:12.421
Good.

30:13.981 --> 30:15.340
Before the evaluation period ends,

30:15.381 --> 30:16.701
maintain your current performance

30:17.701 --> 30:18.740
and don't let me down.

30:19.421 --> 30:19.861
Sure.

30:21.300 --> 30:21.740
By the way,

30:21.941 --> 30:23.461
Sophia loved the dress

30:23.461 --> 30:24.981
from Ms. Xu.

30:25.661 --> 30:26.981
It put her in the spotlight.

30:28.221 --> 30:29.621
Yan is happy

30:29.901 --> 30:31.260
that her aesthetic sense

30:31.500 --> 30:32.528
earns Sophia's approval.

30:32.981 --> 30:33.461
Alright.

30:34.461 --> 30:34.901
Take care.

30:35.020 --> 30:35.621
Take care.

30:55.820 --> 30:56.461
Dr. Yu.

30:58.300 --> 30:59.461
Are you here for Qiao Lin?

31:00.861 --> 31:01.500
She will

31:01.621 --> 31:02.820
be out soon.

31:05.181 --> 31:05.701
Well,

31:06.020 --> 31:07.381
please don't misunderstand.

31:08.340 --> 31:09.861
Yan Studio's accountant fled,

31:09.981 --> 31:10.941
causing chaos.

31:11.540 --> 31:12.461
I'm filling in.

31:15.740 --> 31:17.621
I'm not here to pester Qiao Lin.

31:18.381 --> 31:19.221
I said I'd move on.

31:19.580 --> 31:20.580
I meant it.

31:21.421 --> 31:22.820
I'm genuinely here to help.

31:23.661 --> 31:24.461
Since we met,

31:25.020 --> 31:25.981
I'll make it clear

31:26.221 --> 31:27.020
to you.

31:29.861 --> 31:30.960
Qiao Lin already told me.

31:37.461 --> 31:38.340
I'm truly sorry.

31:38.701 --> 31:40.260
They need an accountant,

31:40.740 --> 31:41.780
and I can be.

31:42.181 --> 31:42.820
Also,

31:45.300 --> 31:46.981
I genuinely need this job.

31:50.141 --> 31:50.861
Finished?

31:51.540 --> 31:52.020
Buddy,

31:52.020 --> 31:53.141
if you need to vent,

31:53.260 --> 31:53.981
hit me.

31:54.181 --> 31:54.820
I'll take it.

32:09.381 --> 32:11.461
You're not holding it against me?

32:12.340 --> 32:14.181
I hope you'll contribute to Yan Studio.

32:15.820 --> 32:16.861
We're adults.

32:17.461 --> 32:18.861
I hope you'll keep your word.

32:20.260 --> 32:21.020
Thank you.

32:21.221 --> 32:22.580
Having a nice chat?

32:25.861 --> 32:26.500
Well,

32:27.300 --> 32:28.461
Dr. Yu is here for you.

32:29.141 --> 32:30.260
I'll leave you two alone.

32:30.701 --> 32:31.141
I'm off.

32:31.740 --> 32:32.141
Bye.

32:32.221 --> 32:32.701
Bye.

32:36.540 --> 32:37.340
I'm sorry.

32:38.540 --> 32:39.340
I should've told you

32:39.340 --> 32:40.580
about Lin Tao working here.

32:40.820 --> 32:42.020
I didn't expect you'd still

32:42.020 --> 32:43.020
clarify things with him.

32:43.500 --> 32:44.181
Thank you

32:44.340 --> 32:45.424
for putting him at ease.

32:45.580 --> 32:46.421
I did that

32:46.421 --> 32:47.740
not for Lin Tao

32:49.181 --> 32:50.461
but for you.

32:51.820 --> 32:52.260
Come on.

32:52.901 --> 32:53.621
Let's get dinner.

32:53.981 --> 32:54.621
- Okay.
- What do you like?

32:55.461 --> 32:56.820
You decide.

32:58.736 --> 33:02.224
♪We embraced under starlight♪

33:03.260 --> 33:04.861
(We must reach the finals)

33:04.901 --> 33:06.352
(and secure a top-eight position.)

33:06.540 --> 33:07.381
(Only then can we)

33:07.381 --> 33:09.500
(get to showcase in the main venue)

33:09.780 --> 33:11.340
(with stage designs)

33:11.340 --> 33:12.540
(that match our entries.)

33:12.901 --> 33:14.300
(This way, Yan Studio's entries)

33:14.381 --> 33:15.701
(will reach wider audiences.)

33:16.304 --> 33:18.352
♪All the year round♪

33:18.736 --> 33:21.232
♪I feel different about you♪

33:21.232 --> 33:23.056
♪My heartbeat races♪

33:23.888 --> 33:26.000
♪See the converging stars♪

33:27.100 --> 33:28.060
(We aim for awards.)

33:28.260 --> 33:29.461
(It's good to have a dream)

33:29.500 --> 33:30.580
(in case it comes true.)

33:36.221 --> 33:37.260
(Must be a gold award.)

33:37.901 --> 33:39.820
(Construction steps breakdown)
(Yes, it must be a gold award.)

33:41.296 --> 33:43.920
♪With you by my side♪

33:43.920 --> 33:47.344
♪Rain or shine♪

33:51.621 --> 33:53.020
I'm not drunk.

33:53.020 --> 33:54.020
I can drink again.

33:54.020 --> 33:56.060
Put me down, and I'll walk by myself.

33:56.181 --> 33:56.941
Exactly.

33:57.264 --> 33:58.060
Just a few drinks.

33:58.060 --> 33:59.381
How could that make you drunk?

33:59.421 --> 34:00.181
That's right.

34:00.740 --> 34:02.260
I can spin around.

34:02.260 --> 34:04.661
Watch me spin.

34:05.100 --> 34:05.901
Not drunk, right?

34:06.141 --> 34:06.861
Impressive, huh?

34:17.072 --> 34:17.680
(Yan Studio)

34:25.623 --> 34:26.672
(25th Qinglan Cup Fashion Design Competition)

34:26.672 --> 34:28.080
♪It's no surprise♪

34:28.080 --> 34:29.968
♪Being happy is so hard♪

34:30.320 --> 34:31.216
(139-Yan Studio)

34:32.816 --> 34:34.672
♪On the day we met again, we said hi♪

34:34.672 --> 34:40.560
♪It was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint♪

34:40.912 --> 34:45.291
♪Who can do anything without regret♪

34:46.128 --> 34:49.584
♪I am all right♪

34:50.832 --> 34:55.152
♪May you live in peace♪

34:55.442 --> 34:57.488
♪Let the world roar♪

34:57.744 --> 34:59.942
♪Sounds like a carnival♪

35:00.190 --> 35:04.368
♪Being alive is never dull♪

35:04.688 --> 35:08.272
(Qinglan Cup National Finals,
Yan Studio)

35:11.941 --> 35:13.261
This is the second-to-last set?

35:13.461 --> 35:13.861
Correct.

35:16.821 --> 35:18.020
This part was well-adjusted.

35:18.341 --> 35:19.220
Previously, I felt

35:19.261 --> 35:20.421
the music tempo was fast.

35:25.264 --> 35:26.416
♪Overcome♪

35:28.620 --> 35:29.100
Beautiful.

35:30.140 --> 35:31.220
Thanks, everyone.

35:31.261 --> 35:32.700
That's all for today.

35:32.781 --> 35:34.180
And get ready for the competition.

35:34.620 --> 35:35.180
Thank you all.

35:35.500 --> 35:36.220
Thank you.

35:36.220 --> 35:36.981
Thank you.

35:37.140 --> 35:37.981
Come here.

35:38.100 --> 35:39.180
Give me the accessories.

35:39.220 --> 35:39.901
I'll do it.

35:41.461 --> 35:42.421
Yan, I'm leaving.

35:43.060 --> 35:44.500
Remember to send me the videos

35:44.500 --> 35:45.140
and photos.

35:45.140 --> 35:45.620
Okay.

35:46.421 --> 35:47.580
Ms. Xu, we're leaving now.

35:47.941 --> 35:48.421
Thank you.

35:48.421 --> 35:50.384
After removing accessories,
go change clothes.

35:52.981 --> 35:54.301
Yan, I'm taking them to change.

35:54.301 --> 35:54.981
Thank you, Yao.

35:55.381 --> 35:55.861
No problem.

35:56.461 --> 35:57.421
Bye, Yan.

35:57.461 --> 35:57.941
I'm off.

35:57.941 --> 35:58.580
Thank you.

35:58.861 --> 35:59.381
Well done.

36:03.461 --> 36:04.461
Well done.

36:04.741 --> 36:05.540
So beautiful.

36:06.060 --> 36:06.580
I'm off.

36:41.500 --> 36:42.580
No issues.

36:47.781 --> 36:49.100
The set design is perfect.

36:50.100 --> 36:50.901
Looks fantastic.

36:52.981 --> 36:54.341
The music works well.

36:55.180 --> 36:56.261
The rhythm is on point.

37:07.381 --> 37:07.901
Exactly.

37:09.220 --> 37:10.100
I didn't feel touched.

37:10.261 --> 37:11.540
No, I didn't.

37:13.341 --> 37:15.220
Then why...?

37:19.781 --> 37:21.341
I think the models performed well.

37:23.341 --> 37:23.821
So why...

37:23.821 --> 37:25.540
Why didn't it move you?

37:44.020 --> 37:46.100
Are you unsatisfied

37:46.100 --> 37:47.020
with this runway show?

37:47.461 --> 37:48.620
Or do you have no confidence

37:48.941 --> 37:49.741
in yourself?

37:49.741 --> 37:50.540
Absolutely not.

37:51.381 --> 37:52.861
I'm very confident in myself.

37:53.901 --> 37:55.461
I'm even more confident in Yan Studio.

37:58.261 --> 37:59.261
Within such a short time,

37:59.261 --> 38:00.140
we've optimized

38:00.540 --> 38:05.341
the lighting, stage design, music,
models, and overall tone

38:05.981 --> 38:07.060
to perfection.

38:07.821 --> 38:08.821
Everything now

38:08.821 --> 38:09.660
looks perfect.

38:12.341 --> 38:13.660
I have watched

38:13.660 --> 38:14.741
today's full rehearsal.

38:15.261 --> 38:16.341
During the presentation,

38:17.060 --> 38:19.461
the outfits are stunning,
and the sets are good.

38:20.020 --> 38:21.100
Everything's excellent,

38:21.341 --> 38:22.981
yet there's an emptiness.

38:23.981 --> 38:25.821
Like there's no connection between them.

38:27.700 --> 38:28.381
As you said,

38:28.901 --> 38:29.741
it didn't move me.

38:31.180 --> 38:32.341
The missing connection

38:32.381 --> 38:34.180
refers to emotional resonance, right?

38:35.781 --> 38:36.180
Exactly.

38:37.140 --> 38:38.060
I want audiences

38:38.981 --> 38:40.620
and judges to not only appreciate

38:41.261 --> 38:41.981
the craftsmanship

38:41.981 --> 38:43.100
in our collection,

38:44.180 --> 38:45.941
but also feel the stories

38:46.901 --> 38:48.620
behind these garments.

38:54.220 --> 38:55.461
I only understand architecture.

38:56.861 --> 38:58.981
But I know
every creator's original intention

38:59.220 --> 39:00.421
stems

39:01.180 --> 39:03.180
from the simplest,

39:03.741 --> 39:04.861
most fundamental hope.

39:05.261 --> 39:06.381
They're emotionally driven.

39:06.781 --> 39:07.821
For example,

39:08.821 --> 39:09.861
the Potala Palace

39:10.901 --> 39:12.580
was built by Songtsen Gampo

39:12.700 --> 39:14.620
for Princess Wencheng.

39:14.861 --> 39:15.381
Of course,

39:15.421 --> 39:17.540
there are
many similar architectural wonders.

39:17.700 --> 39:19.020
The runway setup

39:19.301 --> 39:20.540
creates spatial layers

39:20.660 --> 39:22.100
through dimensional design.

39:22.620 --> 39:24.941
It visually conveys beauty

39:25.461 --> 39:26.421
and evokes emotions.

39:27.261 --> 39:28.060
But things like this

39:28.060 --> 39:29.901
can't impart souls

39:29.941 --> 39:30.741
or emotions.

39:32.981 --> 39:34.180
Do you remember

39:35.060 --> 39:36.461
when you started Yan Studio,

39:36.981 --> 39:38.461
what moved you most?

39:45.100 --> 39:46.941
Yao once mentioned

39:49.461 --> 39:50.941
that every Yi girl,

39:51.660 --> 39:52.741
in the whole process

39:53.540 --> 39:54.301
of growth,

39:54.301 --> 39:55.500
at every significant stage,

39:56.660 --> 39:57.700
has gifts.

39:58.341 --> 39:59.700
Their families craft

40:00.100 --> 40:03.060
special outfits
and dazzling headpieces for them.

40:05.140 --> 40:06.261
Every stitch

40:08.220 --> 40:10.261
carries their love for their children.

40:11.580 --> 40:12.140
Good.

40:13.180 --> 40:14.540
It's something

40:14.660 --> 40:15.901
that can resonate with people.

40:16.981 --> 40:17.821
In the finals,

40:17.901 --> 40:18.660
all teams

40:18.660 --> 40:20.180
showcase technical perfection.

40:20.941 --> 40:23.060
We'll focus on raw emotionality

40:23.660 --> 40:24.781
for the runway presentation.

40:39.301 --> 40:41.381
Grandmothers pass craftsmanship
to mothers,

40:42.020 --> 40:43.461
mothers to daughters.

40:44.901 --> 40:45.901
It's heritage

40:48.821 --> 40:49.700
and evolution.

40:53.381 --> 40:55.421
It's the bloodline connecting

40:57.741 --> 40:59.381
craftspeople to the craftsmanship.

41:13.741 --> 41:14.381
Hello?

41:14.781 --> 41:15.700
Are you home?

41:16.580 --> 41:17.580
Can you gather everyone

41:17.580 --> 41:18.741
for a meeting at the office?

41:19.341 --> 41:20.781
I need to modify our strategy.

41:21.180 --> 41:21.540
Got it.

41:22.341 --> 41:22.981
Appreciate it.

41:37.700 --> 41:38.341
Thank you.

41:41.301 --> 41:41.968
I'll drive you.

41:42.981 --> 41:43.461
Okay.

41:53.840 --> 41:55.280
Blending tradition with modernity,

41:55.280 --> 41:57.060
(Yan Studio reveals
neo-Chinese aesthetics)

41:57.060 --> 41:58.576
(rooted in ethnic cultural essence.)

41:58.576 --> 41:59.620
(Due to the counterfeits,)

41:59.620 --> 42:00.660
(the brand)

42:00.821 --> 42:01.540
(once faced)

42:01.540 --> 42:03.020
(a devastating impact)

42:03.140 --> 42:04.341
(that damaged its reputation)

42:04.341 --> 42:05.821
(and consumer trust.)

42:06.060 --> 42:08.220
(However, through this competition,)

42:08.301 --> 42:09.741
(they've demonstrated)

42:09.741 --> 42:11.981
(a unique design philosophy
and commercial success.)

42:12.100 --> 42:13.020
(Meanwhile,)

42:13.020 --> 42:14.620
(they gained acclaim,)

42:14.861 --> 42:16.261
(won the Commercial Value Award,)

42:16.301 --> 42:18.620
(and achieved miraculous sales growth.)

42:19.100 --> 42:19.540
Cheers.

42:21.941 --> 42:22.700
Guys.

42:23.500 --> 42:24.660
Right now,

42:24.901 --> 42:25.981
let Ms. Xu

42:26.500 --> 42:27.781
speak.

42:28.741 --> 42:29.580
Welcome.

42:32.981 --> 42:33.500
Alright.

42:33.741 --> 42:34.861
On behalf

42:35.461 --> 42:36.341
of Yan Studio,

42:36.381 --> 42:37.620
I'm speaking.

42:38.500 --> 42:39.620
This journey

42:39.620 --> 42:40.901
has been challenging.

42:42.220 --> 42:43.461
I think

42:44.220 --> 42:45.660
we're all aware of that.

42:46.781 --> 42:49.140
Yan Studio's success

42:49.700 --> 42:50.981
belongs to

42:51.540 --> 42:52.821
every team member here.

42:53.060 --> 42:53.861
Thank you all.

42:58.421 --> 42:59.180
What's more,

42:59.461 --> 43:01.781
special gratitude goes

43:03.620 --> 43:04.540
to someone.

43:06.941 --> 43:08.421
Well,

43:10.020 --> 43:11.421
in the lowest moments

43:11.421 --> 43:12.540
of Yan Studio,

43:12.540 --> 43:13.580
he backed us up

43:15.301 --> 43:17.261
and gave us strength.

43:21.381 --> 43:22.580
Thank you, Mr. Liang.

43:24.741 --> 43:25.941
That's our first investor.

43:26.020 --> 43:27.220
Thank you, Mr. Liang.

43:27.821 --> 43:31.821
- Mr. Liang.
- Mr. Liang.

43:32.421 --> 43:33.140
Listen,

43:33.821 --> 43:34.781
I'll continue investing.

43:35.180 --> 43:36.140
The amount will double.

43:38.180 --> 43:39.781
In the coming days, Yan Studio and I

43:39.941 --> 43:40.700
will advance

43:40.821 --> 43:41.901
together.

43:42.781 --> 43:43.381
Also,

43:44.381 --> 43:45.461
after drinking,

43:45.981 --> 43:47.020
we'll have a lucky draw.

43:47.020 --> 43:48.301
No cap on the prize money!

43:50.020 --> 43:50.620
Cheers!

43:50.781 --> 43:54.301
Thank you, Mr. Liang.

43:54.500 --> 43:55.261
Thank you.

43:55.461 --> 43:56.060
Thank you.

43:56.060 --> 43:56.781
So exciting!

43:59.500 --> 44:00.540
There's prize money.

44:02.020 --> 44:02.781
Listen.

44:02.821 --> 44:03.700
There's prize money.

44:06.781 --> 44:08.341
The renowned Spanish designer

44:08.580 --> 44:09.060
Ivan

44:10.100 --> 44:10.981
saw your performance

44:11.020 --> 44:12.341
at the Qinglan Cup competition

44:12.381 --> 44:13.220
and showed interest.

44:13.901 --> 44:14.901
His assistant called me,

44:15.180 --> 44:16.500
saying Ivan wants to meet you.

44:18.421 --> 44:19.540
What's that? Is it good?

44:19.580 --> 44:20.140
Get me one.

44:21.421 --> 44:23.020
I'll inform them later.

44:24.140 --> 44:25.580
So what should we prepare?

44:26.700 --> 44:27.301
Samples,

44:27.381 --> 44:28.781
and have all documents ready.

